---

<section class="final-cta rx">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <span class="cta-eyebrow">Next Step</span>
      <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Fix Your Marketing Operations?</h2>
      <p class="cta-desc">Start with a free audit. We'll spend an hour understanding your situation — your data, your intake process, your vendor landscape — and show you exactly what's costing you.</p>

      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule Free Audit →</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-ghost">Learn More About Us</a>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-contact">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="contact-label">Phone</div>
          <div class="contact-value"><a href="tel:7274833222">727-483-3222</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="contact-label">Email</div>
          <div class="contact-value"><a href="mailto:joe@joehughey.com">joe@joehughey.com</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-item">
          <div class="contact-label">Response Time</div>
          <div class="contact-value">Within 1 business day</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .final-cta {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ink) 0%, var(--navy) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 7vw, 56px);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cta-desc {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 34px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.42);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--glt);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 36px rgba(200, 151, 58, 0.52);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-family: var(--man);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.22s;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .cta-contact {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .contact-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .contact-value {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .contact-value a {
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-value a:hover {
    color: var(--glt);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-ghost {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
